*Probaj* da se opustiš (Try to relax). 
On je *probao* da me zavede (He tried to seduce me). 
*Probala* je novu hranu (She tried a new food). 
Da li ćeš *probati* ovo? (Will you try this?) 
Morate se *probati* da se ljubite (You need to try to kiss). 
*Probaj* da ne misliš previše (Try not to think too much).